All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class SVM
extends Model

Support Vector Machine. It extends Model abstract class.
The implemented SVM is scalable model. It builds a model for each training SampleSet. Then it votes the majority of models with testing SampleSets.
